entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You have successfully rescued the first Alliance Pilot from the Imperial Detainment Facility.
entries.journal_entry_description: Go to the Imperial Detainment Facility and rescue the first Alliance Pilot being held prisoner.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Go back to the Detainment Facility at the Imperial Fortress.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Go back to the Detainment Facility
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Destroy the Battle Droid guards to the Imperial Detainment Facility.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Defeat JH-101 in combat and take his Stormtrooper Armor.
entries.task03_task_display_string_1: You killed the Probot Sentry Droid.
entries.task03_task_display_string_3: You defeated JH-101 and took his Stormtrooper Armor.
entries.task04_comm_message_text: I've sliced JH-101's datapad and now we have a basic idea where all 6 of the prisoners are being held.  Great work.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Search the holding cells located at the West holding wing of the facility. This is somewhere near the front of the Detainment Facility.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Give the pilot the disguise you have.
entries.task08_journal_entry_description: Destroy the Probot Sentry Droid near the Detainment Facility entrance.
entries.task08_journal_entry_title: Take out a Probot Sentry Droid
